rows.label: fev08_140_130_msg0001
rows.name:
I think we're all rested enough.
Let's move out.

rows.label: fev08_140_130_msg0002
rows.name:
We're slowly but surely getting closer
to that World Tree...

rows.label: fev08_140_130_msg0003
rows.name:
Hana just hope Masterpon and others
also heading for World Tree...

rows.label: fev08_140_130_msg0004
rows.name: Hoping is all we can do on that front.

rows.label: fev08_140_130_msg0005
rows.name:
Even if we don't meet up with them
on the way, I think we should wait
a while at the base of the Tree.

rows.label: fev08_140_130_msg0007
rows.name:
What's the holdup?
Are we leaving or not?

rows.label: fev08_140_130_msg0009
rows.name: Honestly, the nerve of this guy...

rows.label: fev08_140_130_msg0010
rows.name:
It looks like the next stage of our
journey will have to be through
that opening.
